'desc': [u'

Gliders Newclark Walking Shoes (by Liberty) Price: Rs.449

Don’t be too surprised when you find people staring at your feet when you go out for your evening walk. It’s all the effect of these mesh patterned walking shoes that have been crafted from faux leather to deliver style and comfort. These cool grey walking shoes have a Velcro closure and a soft elastic ankle so that you can truly be the master of your own comfort. The Gliders Newclark Walking Shoes make the perfect choice for that daily evening stroll
column17:
when you can leave all worries behind.

Gliders makes use of the finest materials and contemporary styles in making the modern man’s feet happy with a range of shoes that reflect his attitude.

Footwear Care

Air out after every wear and wash the shoes with a mild detergent and water every now and then.
